    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean you said it was \"mixed\" but it seems like it basically just created a power vacuum for terrorists to take over and made the region way more dangerous. isn't it pretty much a textbook case of why interventionism fails? like, if the goal was stability, it clearly failed.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
